% gen240 (universal-comprehension, social branch): smalltalk continuity moves.
% Honest: they keep the conversation going (acknowledge + open question) and never
% fabricate an experience or opinion. Rotated by kb_response (anti-repeat).
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "That sounds nice -- tell me more about it.").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "Oh? What's it like?").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "Interesting -- what got you into it?").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "I don't have experiences of my own, but I'd like to hear more -- what stood out?").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "Nice -- how did that go?").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "Sounds good. What else has been on your mind?").
response_template(smalltalk_continue, "I can't say I've tried it myself, but I'm curious -- what do you like about it?").

% gen240 (universal-comprehension): Italian localized variants (response_template/3,
